# Public-repo hygiene: keep compact evidence summaries in Git, but do not track
# raw hardware downloads, provenance databases, scratch packages, or bulky
# generated scratch artifacts by default. Existing tracked files must be removed from
# the index with `git rm --cached`; .gitignore only protects future files.
.maintainer/
Cursor_Audit.md
*_Audit.md
*_audit_private.md
*_handoff.md
*.zip
*.sqlite3
controlled_test_output/**/raw_download*/
controlled_test_output/**/raw_returned_downloads*/
controlled_test_output/**/downloaded_files*/
controlled_test_output/**/_download_intake_originals*/
controlled_test_output/**/raw_hardware_artifacts*/
controlled_test_output/**/raw_reports*/
controlled_test_output/**/spinnaker_reports*/
controlled_test_output/**/reports*/
controlled_test_output/**/ebrains_upload_bundle*/
controlled_test_output/**/stack_trace
controlled_test_output/**/errored
controlled_test_output/**/finished
controlled_test_output/**/*.elf
controlled_test_output/**/*.aplx
controlled_test_output/**/*.o
ebrains_jobs/cra_*/**/__pycache__/
ebrains_jobs/cra_*/**/*.pyc
ebrains_jobs/cra_*/**/*.zip
ebrains_jobs/cra_*/**/*.sqlite3
ebrains_jobs/cra_*/**/*.elf
ebrains_jobs/cra_*/**/*.aplx
ebrains_jobs/cra_*/controlled_test_output/

# Note: controlled_test_output/ is not ignored as a whole. Commit compact,
# claim-bearing reports, manifests, registry files, and summary tables. Raw
# returned hardware archives should be externalized and referenced by manifest.

# Note: ebrains_jobs/ is not ignored as a whole. Commit only compact source-only
# package templates or final source packages that are useful for reproduction.
